---
description: Flux integration rules
globs: lib/flux/**/*,app/**/actions*.ts,app/**/actions/**/*
alwaysApply: false
---

Follow `_contract/flux.md`.

- Use `fluxJson(sub, path, init)` only
- Mint JWT per request; never expose Flux JWT to the browser
- `sub` === `session.user.id` === row `user_id`
